#

Beet Borscht with Sour Cream

60 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy Recipe

Description

A vibrant and hearty soup that combines earthy beets with a touch of creaminess from sour cream, perfect for warming you up on a chilly day.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium
  • potatoes: 2 medium
  • carrots: 1 large
  • onion: 1 medium
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
